106A TA here: You're welcome to pop into Prof Sastry's Content OH to ask about research and big picture things :)
Email the professor and ask? A lot of my professors only made OH info and Zoom links available through bCourse, piazza, or course syllabus so that there's no zoom bombing.

Hi! I'm trying to find days / times / zoom links for virtual OH with Professors Shankar Sastry, Steven Conolly, and Ken Goldberg.

Professor Goldberg's site says Mondays 2-4 via zoom and to check his class syllabus for links but I'm not enrolled + can't find it anywhere online.

The EECS 106a site lists Professor Sastry's Content OH, but I think showing up there to ask about research would be rather disrespectful, so I'd like to attend his general OH.

And couldn't find Professor Conolly's OH anywhere.

I'm emailing all of these professors too but thought it may be quicker to ask here, in case anyone works in their labs!
